title: 349: Jake Shields- MMA Legend
description: Jake Shields is a mixed Martial Artist, American Jiu-Jiutsu Grandmaster, Outdoor Enthusiast and part of the Kimera Koffee team. Jake stopped by the studio on Monday and spoke with Sal, Adam and Justin about fighting, coffee, women and more. More About Jake: Jake is a Strikeforce Middleweight Champ, EliteXC Welterweight Champ, Shoto Welterweight Champ, Rumble on the Rock Welterweight Champ & Tournament Winner.
